10#include <openssl/seed.h>
11
12void SEED_ecb_encrypt(const unsigned char *in, unsigned char *out,
13 const SEED_KEY_SCHEDULE *ks, int enc)
14{
15 if (enc)
16 SEED_encrypt(in, out, ks);
17 else
18 SEED_decrypt(in, out, ks);
19}
